author: Gamers Nexus
description:
Sponsor: Montech HS01 Pro on Amazon https://geni.us/UYLeZn and HS02 Pro https://geni.us/ABM9fEB
Everything is a paid subscription service now, all the way down to data storage. We talk with Wendell of Level1 Techs about taking control of your services, media, internet privacy, and more in this video. Wendell helps to detail some beginner basics on making your own storage server, router, gaming server, your own VPN, family media servers, and more. This is a continuation on the concept that, apparently, you'll own nothing and be happy.

Watch our "Is Intel Actually Screwed?" fun discussion with Wendell here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C3rUP3ULlUQ
Check out our talk about benchmarking Linux with Wendell here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5O6tQYJSEMw
And see his overhaul of our server! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tqndR8435cc

Check out Level1 Techs here! https://www.youtube.com/c/Level1Techs

title: You'll Own Nothing and It's Awful | Taking Control of Your Media, ft. Wendell
